  "id" : "api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe",
  "title" : "DeprecatedCurrencyPipe",
  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"deprecatedcurrencypipe\">DeprecatedCurrencyPipe</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label pipe\">pipe</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/common\">@angular/common</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DeprecatedCurrencyPipe</a> } from <a href=\"api/common\">'@angular/common'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts#L128-L164\">common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n  <th>NgModule</th>\n  <td><a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\"><code>CommonModule</code></a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n<div class=\"what-it-does info-banner\">\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dw2jjfcefffe5w6rkk6vtnrma\">使用区域设置规则将数字格式化为货币。</p>\n\n</div>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n<section class=\"how-to-use\">\n  <h2 id=\"how-to-use\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cflu95twzi71qd095ghj9h0y7\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>使用方法</h2>\n  <p><code>number_expression | currency[:currencyCode[:symbolDisplay[:digitInfo]]]</code></p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e68t0z81gvbv50yfo74u7ln95\">使用 \n<code>currency</code> 将数字格式化为货币。</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cy4mvqwd1ff6v6ddhgm8ydsd\"><code>currencyCode</code> 是 \n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\">ISO 4217</a> 货币代码，例如 \n<code>USD</code> 代表美元，\n<code>EUR</code> 代表欧元。</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"h0po6vio753ugnc6whtilh8v\"><code>symbolDisplay</code> 是一个布尔值，指示是否使用货币符号或代码。</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee341b0dj4jtud42uvia0362e\"><code>true</code>：使用符号（例如 \n<code>$</code>）。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"44yobwkkha14bbnueuptf5iye\"><code>false</code>（默认）：使用代码（例如 \n<code>USD</code>）。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8x4i739jwk9e6fcb1xnyiz3tr\"><code>digitInfo</code> 详细说明请参见 \n<a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe\"><code>DecimalPipe</code></a>。</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"333izjvgszh5ks3bj6sxml41v\">警告：此管道使用国际化 API，该 API 尚未在所有浏览器中可用，可能需要腻子脚本。有关详细信息，请参见 \n<a href=\"guide/browser-support\">浏览器支持</a>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"example\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"lzz2v4ucg07faxnpe2bu1wa1\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>范例</h3>\n<code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'deprecated-currency-pipe',\n  template: `&lt;div&gt;\n    &lt;!--output 'CAD0.26'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;A: {{<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> | currency:'CAD'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output '$0,001.35'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{b | currency:'CAD':true:'4.2-2'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;`\n})\nexport class DeprecatedCurrencyPipeComponent {\n  <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a>: number = 0.259;\n  b: number = 1.3495;\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - guide/browser-support\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n - api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#deprecatedcurrencypipe\n - api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#description\n - api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#example\n - api/common/DeprecatedCurrencyPipe#how-to-use\n - api/core/Component\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - guide/browser-support\n - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts#L128-L164\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/common\n-->"
}